@startuml
title UC06 - Feedback
actor Student
actor Tutor
participant FE as Frontend
participant FB as FeedbackAPI
database FbDB
participant Sess as SessionAPI
participant Notif

Student -> FE: Open Feedback
FE -> Sess: GET completed sessions
Sess --> FE: list
Student -> FE: Choose session + ratings
FE -> FB: POST /feedback
FB -> FbDB: save published
FB -> Notif: feedback_received to Tutor
FB --> FE: 201

Tutor -> FE: Open tutor feedback page
FE -> FB: GET /tutor/feedback
FB --> FE: list + stats
Tutor -> FE: Mark viewed
FE -> FB: PATCH /tutor/feedback/:id/mark-viewed
FB -> FbDB: tutorViewed=true
FB --> FE: 200
@enduml
